'''飓风奥菲莉亚'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Ophelia}}）是[[2011年大西洋飓风季|2011年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第17个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]、第16场热带风暴、第四场飓风和第三场[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]，也是本季的最强飓风。系统源自中大西洋的[[东风波|东风波]]，于9月17日在[[佛得角|佛得角群岛]]和[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]之间的中途海域附近成形，之后总体向[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，于9月21日升级成热带风暴，再于次日达到持续风速每小时100公里的首波强度高峰。接下来气旋因行经洋面[[风切变|风切变]]增多而开始减弱，于9月25日退化成残留[[低气压|低气压区]]。26日，系统残留又因风切变减少而重新组织，促使[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于9月27日再度开始针对系统发布公告。气旋转向北上，于9月28日清晨再度达到热带风暴标准，然后[[快速增强|快速增强]]，于数天后达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]220公里的最高强度。此后飓风因行经洋面[[海面温度|水温]]降低而弱化，并开始逐渐向[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]转变，于10月3日完成转变过程。

奥菲莉亚发展成形后，气象机构向加勒比群岛东北部发布多份[[热带气旋警告|风暴观察预警和警告]]，有关部门敦促当地居民做好应对狂风暴雨的准备。气旋到达距群岛最近的位置时已产生数英寸雨量，引发多起[[泥石流|泥石流]]，路上有多人需要外界救援。[[百慕大|百慕大]]测得的降雨总量不高，阵风时速也低于热带风暴标准，但[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]及危险的[[离岸流|离岸流]]在沿海地区产生轻度破坏。[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]因暴雨引发洪灾，许多建筑及多条道路被毁。奥菲莉亚转变成温带气旋后，欧洲各地居民接到警报，部分区域准备应对时速可能超过120公里的狂风和累积超过100毫米雨量。受风暴湿气及寒冷天气的共同影响，[[爱尔兰岛|爱尔兰岛]]北部降下数英寸厚的雪，数百户居民家中断电。总体而言，奥菲莉亚没有造成人员丧生，破坏程度也很轻微。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Ophelia 2011 track.png}}
9月中旬，一股[[东风波|东风波]]从非洲西海进入大西洋低纬度海域向西移动，并开始同[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]相互影响，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]在48小时热带天气展望中称系统有望发展成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，但可能性并不高<ref>{{cite report | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = Stacy Stewart | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109172340/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109172340 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041340/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109172340/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109172340 | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|FL]] | dead-url = no }}</ref>。外界大气环境中的[[风切变|风切变]]对系统发展倾向有利，系统云层格局有所改善，还发展出关联的地面[[低气压|低气压区]]。[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]总体向西行进，其中不断有[[对流|对流]]活动爆发，气象机构9月19日清晨发布的热带天气展望认为系统很可能会发展成热带气旋。<ref>{{cite report | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-09-19 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = Stacy Stewart | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041611/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109190539/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109190539 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109190539/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109190539 }}</ref>根据卫星对系统发展趋势的估算和[[散射仪|高级散射仪]]所测数据，美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]次日18点将位于[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]以东约2090公里海域的扰动天气升级成热带低气压，再于6小时后将之升级成热带风暴并以“奥菲莉亚”（{{lang|en|Ophelia}}）命名。<ref name="OpheliaTCR">{{cite report | title = Hurricane Ophelia Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-12-08 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = John Cangialosi | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL162011_Ophelia.pdf | deadurl = no | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084202/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL162011_Ophelia.pdf }}</ref>

[[File:Tropical_Storm_Ophelia_Sept_28_2011_1705Z.jpg|thumb]]附近的热带风暴奥菲莉亚。]]

风暴在朝西北偏西方向前进的同时继续增强，气旋北侧半圆内逐渐形成明显的弧形对流带，中心附近还发展出深层对流<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Ophelia Discussion Number 2 | date = 2011-09-21 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = Daniel Brown | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.002.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307160234/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-07 }}</ref>。不过，此次强化过程的持续时间很短，附近的[[冷心低压|上层低气压区]]致使风切变增多，导致奥菲莉亚的部分下层环流中心暴露在外。虽然从卫星图像上看系统的层次结构较为混乱，但附近海域的浮标所测数据却表明气旋强度高过此前预期，9月22日时的最大持续风速达到每小时100公里。随着上层低气压区逐渐逼近，风暴外界环境中的风切变越来越多，导致气旋中的对流几乎被完全剥离。9月23日清晨，系统的深层对流已大幅消退，但当天下午又卷土重来，[[飓风猎人|空军预备役侦察机]]发现其风速达到每小时95公里，比气象部门此前估计的75公里要高得多。这一强度未能长久保持，奥菲莉亚的云层格局再度变得混乱无章。9月25日清晨时分，系统的下层环流中心再度暴露出来，而且也已长时间没有对流活动发展，美国国家飓风中心据此宣布行进至[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]北部以东约290公里洋面的气旋已退化成残留低气压区。<ref name="OpheliaTCR" />

9月25日下午，系统残留的下层中心消散，但层次分明的中层中心仍在坚持。气象机构起初认为这些残留再生的可能性很小，也不大可能再出现深层对流爆发<ref>{{cite report | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-09-26 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = John Cangialosi | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109260600/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109260600 | deadurl = no | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091756/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109260600/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109260600 }}</ref>，但到了9月26日下午，热带天气展望中预计的再生可能已提升至30%<ref>{{cite report | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-09-26 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | deadurl = no | author = Richard Pasch | location = Miami, FL | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304220521/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109261740/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109261740 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109261740/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109261740 }}</ref>。组织良好的云块内发展出新的下层环流，气象部门当晚在预报中称系统很可能再度成为热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2011-09-26 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = Robbie Berg | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151022155019/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109262339/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109262339 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201109262339/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201109262339 | location = Miami, FL | archivedate = 2015-10-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。经过发入系统的空军预备役侦察机确认，美国国家飓风中心于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月27日中午12点再度将热带扰动归类成热带低气压奥菲莉亚，并在18小时后第二次将其升级成热带风暴，宣布气旋的最大持续风速已提升至每小时75公里。抵达覆盖整个中大西洋的[[副热带高压脊|副热带高压脊]]西部边缘后，奥菲莉亚开始蜿蜒北上并再度强化，9月28日晚，中心上空已有深层对流爆发，微波卫星图像显示风暴已发展出[[风眼|风眼]]。<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Storm Ophelia Discussion Number 26 | date = 2011-09-28 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = Eric Blake | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055958/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.026.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.026.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>9月29日下午，气旋的上层[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]已向各方位扩展<ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Ophelia Discussion Number 29 | date = 2011-09-29 | accessdate = 2016-05-08 | author = Lixion Avila | work = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.029.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | location = Miami, FL | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306211015/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.029.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration }}</ref>，卫星强度估算结果也持续上升，美国国家飓风中心为此于{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点把奥菲莉亚升级成一级飓风<ref name="OpheliaTCR" />。

9月30日，风暴出人意料地进入[[快速增强|快速增强期]]，卫星图像上的风眼也变得非常清晰<ref>{{cite report | title = Hurricane Ophelia Discussion Number 31 | date = 2011-09-30 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | author = Stacy Stewart | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307154332/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.031.shtml | deadurl = no | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.discus.031.shtml? }}</ref>。截至{{lang|en|UTC}}早上6点，气旋已增强成二级飓风，再于12小时后成为[[2011年大西洋飓风季|2011年大西洋飓风季]]第三场[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]。10月1日晚，奥菲莉亚风眼墙的顶端云系温度继续下降，风眼顶端的云层温度相应升高。{{lang|en|UTC}}10月2日凌晨0点，风暴在从[[百慕大|百慕大]]以东洋面经过期间达到四级飓风标准，并于几乎同一时间达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]220公里、最低[[气压|气压]]940[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.76[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。次日，飓风因行经海域水温降低、大气环境理为稳定而开始减弱。截至{{lang|en|UTC}}下午18点已降至低于大型飓风强度下限，再于{{lang|en|UTC}}10月3日早上6点降级成热带风暴。四小时后，奥菲莉亚在行进至[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]以西洋面时完全失去热带天气系统特征，气象部门宣布系统已转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]。次日下午，奥菲莉亚的温带残留低气压区被更大规模的天气系统吸收。<ref name="OpheliaTCR" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Hurricane_Ophelia_Oct_2_2011_1505Z.jpg|thumb]]
虽然奥菲莉亚的中心仍在小安的列斯群岛以东约330公里海域<ref>{{cite report | author = John Cangialosi | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-09-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306210021/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.public.023.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Tropical Depression Ophelia Public Advisory Number 23 | location = Miami, FL | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.public.023.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>，但其外围[[雨带|外围雨带]]还是令当地普降暴雨。[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]部分地区降下超过100毫米雨量，导致多条河流沿线泛滥成灾。该国有近1600人被困，许多汽车被洪水冲走，还有多地发生[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，导致许多社区同外界的交通中断。<ref>{{cite news | author = TDN Wire Staff | work = The Dominican | date = 2011-09-28 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Flooding and landslides in Dominica during heavy rainfall | archivedate = 2016-03-10 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310181742/http://www.thedominican.net/2011/09/heavy-flooding-in-dominica.html | url = http://www.thedominican.net/2011/09/heavy-flooding-in-dominica.html }}</ref>多家商铺和学校赶在风暴来袭前关闭<ref>{{cite news |publisher=Caribbean Broadcasting Cooperation |deadurl=yes |date=2011-09-29 |accessdate=2013-02-19 |author=Staff Writer |title=Dominica Schools closed in Ophelia's wake |url=http://www.cbc.bb/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2829:dominica-schools-closed-in-ophelias-wake&catid=37:regional&Itemid=93 |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130219174541/http://www.cbc.bb/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=2829:dominica-schools-closed-in-ophelias-wake&catid=37:regional&Itemid=93 |archivedate=2013-02-19 }}</ref>。飓风行进至距该国最近的位置时，坎恩菲尔德机场已被暴雨淹没，许多道路、建筑和农场受损，部分居民被困。当地阵风时速有时会达到60公里，[[瓜德罗普|瓜德罗普]]部分地区还出现[[雷暴|雷暴]]天气<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | publisher = France-Antilles | date = 2011-09-29 | accessdate = 2012-03-31 | title = Encore en jaune pour fortes pluies et orages! | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120331173028/http://www.guadeloupe.franceantilles.fr/actualite/education-sante-environnement/encore-en-jaune-pour-fortes-pluies-et-orages-29-09-2011-140212.php | archivedate = 2012-03-31 | url = http://www.guadeloupe.franceantilles.fr/actualite/education-sante-environnement/encore-en-jaune-pour-fortes-pluies-et-orages-29-09-2011-140212.php }}</ref>。

9月29日气旋升级成飓风后，百慕大气象局向全岛发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308063825/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.public.029.shtml | date = 2011-09-29 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Hurricane Ophelia Public Advisory Number 29 | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.public.029.shtml? | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。接下来几天里，气象机构预计奥菲莉亚的移动路线会向东侧偏移，百慕大遭受破坏性风速影响的可能逐渐降低，该岛最终得以免遭飓风的直接袭击。百慕大气象局因此在10月1日晚中止之前发布的热带风暴观察预警<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Eric Blake | author2 = Michael Brennan | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-10-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Hurricane Ophelia Tropical Cyclone Update | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.update.10012220.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308054952/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.update.10012220.shtml | deadurl = no | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。受气旋影响，4架次美国飞往百慕大的航班取消。该国的马蹄海滩临时关闭，南海岸全部收到大浪警报，此外还有多项体育赛事延期。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = The Royal Gazette | date = 2011-10-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Flights cancelled, beach closed by Ophelia | url = http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20111001/NEWS/111009997/1001 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120103220839/http://www.royalgazette.com/article/20111001/NEWS/111009997/1001 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-01-03 }}</ref>途径百慕大以东约220公里海域期间，风暴的外围雨带产生约10毫米雨量，岛上各地阵风时速最高为55公里<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Bermuda Weather Service | date = 2011-10-02 | accessdate = 2011-10-03 | title = October 1, 2011, Climate Report | url = http://www.weather.bm/climatereport/climateReport.asp | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111003155227/http://www.weather.bm/climatereport/climateReport.asp | archivedate = 2011-10-03 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

10月1日，[[加拿大环境部|加拿大环境部]]向[[阿瓦隆半岛|阿瓦隆半岛]]发布热带风暴观察预警<ref>{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-10-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223616/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.public.037.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Hurricane Ophelia Public Advisory Number 37 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2011/al16/al162011.public.037.shtml? | location = Miami, FL }}</ref>。纽芬兰岛各地居民收到警告，称降水有可能达到100毫米<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | publisher = CBC News | date = 2011-10-01 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Hurricane Ophelia heads to Newfoundland, Nova Scotia | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141011171044/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/hurricane-ophelia-heads-to-newfoundland-nova-scotia-1.1048175 | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/hurricane-ophelia-heads-to-newfoundland-nova-scotia-1.1048175 | archivedate = 2014-10-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。该岛曾于一年多以前受到[[飓风伊戈尔|飓风伊戈尔]]重创，此次奥菲莉亚来袭产生的影响表明当地的修复工作还存在些许不足之处。[[布林半岛|布林半岛]]和[[波纳威斯塔半岛|波纳威斯塔半岛]]有六条道路在风暴期间暂时封闭，有两项工程受到严重破坏，伊戈尔过后修筑的多个[[涵洞|涵洞]]被奥菲莉亚引发的洪水冲毁。<ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | publisher = CBC News | date = 2011-10-04 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Igor damage wasn't fixed well: mayor | url = http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/newfoundland-labrador/igor-damage-wasn-t-fixed-well-mayor-1.1077052 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151222125746/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/newfoundland-labrador/igor-damage-wasn-t-fixed-well-mayor-1.1077052 | archivedate = 2015-12-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

奥菲莉亚袭击纽芬兰岛期间，英国的气象学家已开始提醒居民，风暴残留可能会在数天内给该国带去不稳定天气<ref>{{cite news | author = Heidi Blake | title = North braced for Hurricane Ophelia as south basks in record-breaking heat | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | newspaper = The Telegraph | date = 2011-10-02 | archivedate = 2014-02-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140225090008/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/topics/weather/8802629/North-braced-for-Hurricane-Ophelia-as-south-basks-in-record-breaking-heat.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/weather/8802629/North-braced-for-Hurricane-Ophelia-as-south-basks-in-record-breaking-heat.html }}</ref>。英国此时正经受创纪录的[[2011年秋英国热浪|热浪]]袭击，以29.9[[摄氏度|°C]]刷新史上10月最高气温纪录，新闻报导中称奥菲莉亚的残留会令全国范围气温大幅下降<ref>{{cite news | author = Luke Salkeld | title = After a scorching weekend, get ready for SNOW and a HURRICANE as temperatures drop 18c by Friday | date = 2011-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304073623/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2044601/UK-weather-Get-ready-SNOW-HURRICANE-temperatures-drop-18c-Friday.html | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | newspaper = Daily Mail | deadurl = no | url = http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-2044601/UK-weather-Get-ready-SNOW-HURRICANE-temperatures-drop-18c-Friday.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。报导中预计系统会产生狂风暴雨，多地的轮渡服务因此取消。此外，风暴残留导致的气温骤降还有可能在英国各地产生降雪<ref>{{cite news | author = Richard James | publisher = Metro News United Kingdom | date = 2011-10-03 | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | title = Britain set for heavy rain and snow as Hurricane Ophelia ends mini heatwave | archivedate = 2016-05-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160502224621/http://metro.co.uk/2011/10/03/britain-set-for-heavy-rain-and-snow-as-hurricane-ophelia-ends-mini-heatwave-170753/ | url = http://metro.co.uk/2011/10/03/britain-set-for-heavy-rain-and-snow-as-hurricane-ophelia-ends-mini-heatwave-170753/ }}</ref>。最终，[[多尼戈尔|多尼戈尔]]（{{lang|en|Donegal}}）降下本季第一场雪，有数英寸厚，致使数以百计的居民失去供电<ref name="snow">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | publisher = DonegalDaily | title = Almost 1,0000 homes left without electricity as rain, gales and snow hits Donegal | accessdate = 2016-05-09 | date = 2011-10-06 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304030618/http://www.donegaldaily.com/2011/10/06/almost-1000-homes-left-without-electricity-as-rain-gales-and-snow-hits-donegal/ | url = http://www.donegaldaily.com/2011/10/06/almost-1000-homes-left-without-electricity-as-rain-gales-and-snow-hits-donegal/ }}</ref>。

